1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,640
Firefighters are real life heroes in our city.

2
00:00:04,640 --> 00:00:10,160
When there is a fire, they arrive quickly in a big red truck.

3
00:00:10,160 --> 00:00:15,520
They wear heavy clothes and use long hoses to spray water.

4
00:00:15,520 --> 00:00:18,560
Their job is extremely dangerous.

5
00:00:18,560 --> 00:00:22,400
However, they are very brave and strong.

6
00:00:22,400 --> 00:00:28,000
I admire them, so I want to help people like them in the future.

